  "title": "Marketing Intern(Content Creation- Tik Tok & Instagram)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Location : Remote</strong><br /><strong>Commitment : 3-6 months full time / Part Time Internship</strong><br />\n<strong>About the Role</strong><br />We’re expanding our online presence and seeking a creative marketing intern who’s fluent in TikTok trends, Instagram aesthetics, and culture-driven storytelling.</p><p>This is a fully remote position, giving you the freedom to choose where and how you work while helping grow our brand’s awareness and engagement.</p><p>While technical skills like Photoshop and video editing are a plus, what matters most is your creativity, eye for design, and self-driven attitude to learn and contribute.</p><p><strong>Role Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Conceptualize film, and edit 20 TikTok videos per month (product showcases, behind-the-scenes, styling, etc.)</li><li>Create and schedule 12 Instagram posts per month (feed posts and reels)</li><li>Propose and pitch creative concepts that align with our brand tone</li><li>Stay up to data on social media trends and best practices</li><li>Maintain visual and narrative consistency across platforms</li><li>Collaborate with the team for upcoming launches, events, or giveaways </li></ul><p><br /><strong>KPI- Based Reward</strong><br />You will be rewarded <strong>an additional S$100 for every 100 followers </strong>gained per platform(Tik Toc & Instagram), calculated monthly, based on real growth and engagement metrics.<br />\n<br /><strong>Who You Are</strong></p><ul><li>Don't wait to be tied down to set work times</li><li>Experience with TikToK and instagram content creation(portfolio or account link is a plus)</li><li>Have existing skills or willing to learn basic video and photo editing</li><li>Independent,creative, and deadline-oriented.</li></ul>",
